\n  政府今日（二月八日）刊登憲報修訂《公眾衞生(動物及禽鳥)(禽畜飼養的發牌)規例》及《廢物處置條例》以禁止散養家禽活動。新法例下星期一（二月十三日） 正式生效。<br />\n<br />\n  衞生福利及食物局發言人說，新法例旨在保障公眾健康及減低香港爆發禽流感的風險。<br />\n<br />\n  法例經修訂後，市民將不准散養任何家禽。任何人士如未經許可而散養活家禽 － 雞、鴨、鵝、鴿和鵪鶉 － 均屬違法，違者可被罰款五萬至十萬元。<br />\n<br />\n  發言人補充說：「政府會成立巡邏隊伍，確保有關法例得以落實。現時家有散養家禽的市民，請勿再飼養，如需政府協助可致電政府熱線1823。」<br />\n<br />\n完<br />\n<br />\n２００６年２月８日（星期三）<br />\n香港時間１１時０３分"},{"pid":"2cd33519af7f8de4b51341e2770182c7a1dd89f7","tid":2126661,"uid":266336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db453f3d804d811dde5bafdfb830ae62b930dbc9","tid":2126661,"uid":46587,"like":14,"dislike":4,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T10:58:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F21%2F155703_54ea7bb232abc5a9a958394442e043d6.png&amp;h=43e37a2e&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV8Bfiga.png&amp;h=c7181449&amp;s=540\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:01:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa741f48804be8cd2edfdf2645cac1cd0e8c9e25","tid":2126661,"uid":116696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80235997129e7e2a707a27f94fc9872b4b81f39b","tid":2126661,"uid":42762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T10:57:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tPg0i1biOHM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtPg0i1biOHM&d=EOe11knUQePtQJIakN8qx7M5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=0d30f563\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tPg0i1biOHM</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yX0r-av6Cp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyX0r-av6Cp4&d=EOe11knUQePtQJIakN8qx7M5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=c16546a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yX0r-av6Cp4</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-